  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>Curled within the shell is a hungry wormlet, its coils rippling restlessly.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be <span class=\"name name-fuel\">cursed</span> and <span class=\"name name-fuel\">insatiable</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的、可生育的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>壳里蜷缩着一条饥肠辘辘的小虫，正在不安地扭动。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-fuel\">受到诅咒</span>以及<span class=\"name name-fuel\">贪心</span>的基因潜质。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">正準備孵化！</span><br><br>蜷縮在殼內的是一隻飢餓的幼蟲，尾部不安份地微微起伏著。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物從潛在基因看來，可能具有<span class=\"name name-fuel\">受詛咒</span>且<span class=\"name name-fuel\">貪得無厭</span>的特徵。"
  },
